🧩 6️⃣ After Login — Response Handling

ADFS authenticates user
Then POSTs SAMLResponse to:

/saml/consume


🔹 Step 2: Consume Action

  def consume

      response = OneLogin::RubySaml::Response.new(
      params[:SAMLResponse],
      settings: SAML_SETTINGS
    )
    end

This:

	Decodes Base64

	Parses XML

	Prepares for validation

🔹 Step 3: Validate Response

	  unless response.is_valid?
      raise "Invalid SAML Response"
    end

This checks:

	Signature

	Expiry

	Audience

	Issuer

	Certificate

	Replay attack

	VERY CRITICAL LINE.

